div.p: For exceptions WITHOUT error code: asm push dword 0 ; Fake error code push dword N ; ISR number
For exceptions WITH error code: asm push dword N ; ISR number only
pusha instruction pushes: EDI, ESI, EBP, ESP, EBX, EDX, ECX, EAX Note: ESP pushed is value BEFORE pusha
Manual segment register saves: asm push ds push es push fs push gs mov ax, 0x10 ; Load kernel DS mov ds, ax mov es, ax mov fs, ax mov gs, ax push esp ; Pass stack pointer call isr_common_handler
Restoration sequence: asm add esp, 4 ; Remove arg pointer pop gs pop fs pop es pop ds popa ; Restore general regs add esp, 8 ; Remove err_code + int_no iret ; Return from interrupt
